  "title": "Nuka-Isles",
  "description": "A Fallout Mod for Minecraft",
  "body": "<p><img style=\"display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;\" src=\"https://github.com/SkarMC/NukaIslesStorage/blob/main/rawd.png?raw=true\" width=\"500\" height=\"114\" /></p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<hr />\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\">&nbsp;</p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\">Currently, Nuka-Isles only adds scrap metal tools and armor, Nuka-Cola, and the Nuka-Cola Machine. </span></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\">As time goes on more will be added as we plan to bring as much as we can from the Fallout universe into Minecraft.</span></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\">&nbsp;</p>\n<hr />\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 24px;\"><strong>Getting Started</strong></span></p>\n<div class=\"spoiler\">\n<p>Scrap Metal can be used to craft many items and may be useful if you don't have enough iron.</p>\n<p><img src=\"https://github.com/SkarMC/NukaIslesStorage/blob/main/5.png?raw=true\" width=\"300\" height=\"150\" /></p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p>One such item is the Nuka-Cola Machine.</p>\n<p><img src=\"https://github.com/SkarMC/NukaIslesStorage/blob/main/1.png?raw=true\" width=\"300\" height=\"150\" /></p>\n<p><img src=\"https://github.com/SkarMC/NukaIslesStorage/blob/main/7.png?raw=true\" width=\"187\" height=\"300\" /></p>\n<p>With the Nuka-Cola Machine, you can store and chill Nuka-Cola for greater effects.</p>\n<p>You can drink Nuka-Cola or shift-click the machine to get caps which you can trade with Villagers.</p>\n<p><br /><img src=\"https://github.com/SkarMC/NukaIslesStorage/blob/main/2.png?raw=true\" width=\"350\" height=\"151\" /></p>\n</div>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<hr />\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 24px;\"><strong><b>Credits</b></strong></span></p>\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\"><a href=\"https://legacy.curseforge.com/members/wafflewarriortm/projects\"><b>Waffle Warrior</b></a><b> - Textures</b></span></p>\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\"><b><a href=\"https://legacy.curseforge.com/members/fiskfillear/projects\">FiskFille</a> - Code Assistance</b></span></p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<hr />\n<p><a href=\"https://discord.gg/PzSn6pu56a\"><img style=\"display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;\" src=\"https://github.com/SkarMC/NukaIslesStorage/blob/main/E3fGoAf.png?raw=true\" width=\"400\" height=\"128\" /></a></p>",
